            "abstract": [
                "Scytale of Sparta -- Substitution Ciphers -- Caesar Cipher -- ROT-13 -- Atbash Cipher -- Vigen\u00e8re Cipher -- Playfair -- Hill 2x2 -- Column Transposition -- Affine Cipher -- Summary -- Chapter 4 Cryptographic Math and Frequency Analysis -- Modular Arithmetic and the Greatest Common Devisor -- Prime Numbers -- Prime Number Theorem -- School Primality Test -- Fermat's Little Theorem -- Miller-Rabin Primality Test -- Generate Large Prime Numbers -- Basic Group Theory -- Orders of Elements -- Modular Inverses -- Fermat's Little Theorem to Find the Inverse -- Extending the GCD -- Euler's Theorem",
